#

Mushroom Risotto with Truffle Oil

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyMushrooms

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

Creamy risotto infused with earthy mushrooms and a luxurious drizzle of truffle oil for an elevated dining experience.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • Mushrooms (cremini or shiitake): 2 cups, sliced
  • Shallots: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • White wine: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
